summary: This document is a certified record of birth issued by the Commonwealth of Massachusetts, specifically from the Registry of Vital Records and Statistics. It includes a certification by the Registrar of Vital Records and Statistics, Karin A. Barrett, confirming the authenticity of the record. The document is subject to protective orders and contains security features.

persons.name: Karin A. Barrett
persons.role: Registrar of Vital Records and Statistics
persons.context: Karin A. Barrett is identified as the Registrar who certifies the authenticity of the birth record.

keyFacts: The document is a certified record of birth.
Karin A. Barrett is the Registrar of Vital Records and Statistics.
The document is subject to protective orders.
It contains security features to prevent alteration or reproduction.
